# Contributing to [ppm_sic]

Thank you for considering contributing to [Your Project Name]! This document outlines some guidelines to help you get started.

## Table of Contents

- [Reporting Bugs](#reporting-bugs)
- [Submitting Feature Requests](#submitting-feature-requests)
- [Code Contribution Guidelines](#code-contribution-guidelines)
  - [Branching](#branching)
